@NODE "H"  "Hydrogen"
Name of the element : Hydrogen
Latin name          : Hydrogenium
German name         : Wasserstoff
French name         : Hydrogčne

Symbol              : H
Atomic number       : 1
Isotopes            : @{" Overview " link ISOTOP_H}
State at 25°C       : gaseous, non-metal
Abundance [p.p.m.]  : 1520
Discovered by       : Cavendish (1766)

