@NODE "KURZ_BE"  "Short Description of PSE V 1.2 "

PSE V 1.2 is a periodic system of elements in Amigaguide format. You can click
on any element to get extendet information.

PSE V1.2 contains the most important data of an element such as rel. atomic mass,
electron configuration, density, oxidation states, and others.

It is meant as a small help for all who needs a PSE in daily work.
@next MAIN
@prev MAIN
@ENDNODE
@NODE "WERBUNG"  "Advertizing"

There are other products of me:

JABBA.GUIDE V 1.0 (Aminet     : games/roleplay/jabba.lha)

An adventure for AD&D II roleplaying syste of TSR. Using AmigaGuide format
should reduce usuable paper chaos, aiding rolemaster to concentrate at the
adventure itself. The module is designed for characters up to 5th level of
experience.
Sorry, currently german only.


                         UNDER DEVELOPMENT!!!

Currently under development are:

- Porting of PSE12.guide to HTML.
    (PSE V 1.2 will be the last Version in AmigaGuid format)

- a HowTo for building UIPAC-names of organic compound substances using
  HTML (It is much better in including graphics in text! :-)

- Port of JABBA.GUIDE to HTML.

