@NODE "PROBLEME" "Known Problems"

The table is shown wrong

Unfortunatly AmigaGuide doesn't support tables.
The display of the table depends on a fixed font with width 6.
So the MultiView version of this guide forces a Topay/8 font at the first
page. Other viewers should be called with such a font as system font.

Using Topaz 8 is always a way to correct this problem ;-)

Note of the author:

If OS <= 2.1 use PSE.GUIDE.

If OS >= 3.0 use PSE_MV_E.GUIDE, cause it uses some extensions not available
before.

